'''Authority Officers''' were the members of the [[Indu Council]]'s security force, the [[Council Authority]]. They were responsible for protecting and maintaining order within the Council.

One Authority Officer, [[Kaleb Darme]], was responsible for the assassination of chief [[councillor]] [[Shek Barayel]] and the subsequent murder of his [[Aide/Legends|aide]], [[Tev Aden]].

